==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pineapple
<hw>Pine"ap`ple</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A tropical plant (<spn>Ananassa sativa</spn>); also, its fruit; --
so called from the resemblance of the latter, in shape and external
appearance, to the cone of the pine tree. Its origin is unknown, though
conjectured to be American.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pineaster</ent>⟦br⟧
